From the Infowars web site ::

Alex welcomes back to the show Ben Fuchs, the host of the nationally syndicated radio program on GCN, "The Bright Side." Fuchs is a registered pharmacist, nutritionist, cosmetic chemist and founder of EconoComp Pharmacy and Rocky Mountain Natural Laboratories [and one of Alex's partners in his online supplement marketing business, infowarsteam.com]. 

Alex also covers the latest news on the economy, including the significant downgrading of major banks in France as the eurozone heads for a spin-out.
